'''A_M_FireCGun''' (bool ''accurate'')<br>

Does nothing if the calling actor has no valid target.

Otherwise, plays the sound "weapons/chngun" on the WEAPON channel, calls [[A_FaceTarget]], then performs a missile-range hitscan attack without spread (if ''accurate'' is true) or a horizontal spread of 5.625Â° (if ''accurate'' is false) that inflicts 5d3 damage and spawns a {{Class|BulletPuff}}. This replicates {{Class|Chaingun}} [[A_FireCGun|fire]].

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|ScriptedMarine}} and derived classes.

